#summary Golf Markup Language Documentation: complexType Placemarks.

== Name ==

*[CPlacemarks Placemarks]*

  	

===  Super Types ===
{{{
anyType
  |
  +--Placemarks (restriction)
}}}
----
    

===  Documentation ===
        
			Placemarks is a collection of points and/or areas of interest.
		
  	
===  Properties ===

  	This component is not nillable.
---- 	
        
===  Model ===

	<...>  ([CPointOfInterest poi] | [CAreaOfInterest aoi])`*` </...>

----
    

=== Nested Element Summary ===
        
|| [CAreaOfInterest golfml:AreaOfInterest] || [CAreaOfInterest aoi] ||  					Area of interest.				 ||
|| [CPointOfInterest golfml:PointOfInterest] || [CPointOfInterest poi] ||  					Point of interest.				 ||

===  Local Usage ===

    	[CHole Hole]
----
    <xs:complexType name="Placemarks">  <xs:choice maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0">    <xs:element name="poi" type="golfml:PointOfInterest">    </xs:element>    <xs:element name="aoi" type="golfml:AreaOfInterest">    </xs:element>  </xs:choice></xs:complexType>
----
